{"id": "1479567233343819776", "channel_id": "1479428860591210528", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "@everyone 大家的意见我们收到了。值得一提的是，皮克曼回调后广受好评的版本，正是出自阿拉克涅这次新立绘的同一位画师之手。这位画师是长期为《忘却前夜》贡献立绘的创作者，但我们也意识到，如何在每个设计中更好地回应大家的期待，是我们需要持续深入研究的课题。我们会认真参考大家的反馈，在正式放出前于内部进行评估。\n\nWe have received everyone's feedback. It is worth mentioning that the version of Pickman which was well-received after the revision was created by the same artist behind Arachne's new art. This artist has been a long-term contributor to Morimens, and we recognize that how we better meet everyone's expectations with each design is something we need to continue studying carefully. We will take your feedback seriously and conduct an internal review before the final release.", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T19:51:57.459000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Ogier_Cheerup", "emoji_id": "1468259351889318049", "count": 24}, {"emoji": "GDoll_Inferno_serenity", "emoji_id": "1468257540809822302", "count": 10}, {"emoji": "angry3", "emoji_id": "1356053026863058994", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
